FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781197569
OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,FHealey is the fourth Cabinet minister
OL,7,Fto leave Starmer's government since
OL,8,Fcoming to power - and the second to
OL,9,Fresign over policy differences after
OL,10,FWes Streeting quit as health secretary
OL,11,Flast month amid the fallout from
OL,12,FLabour's local election losses.
OL,14,FStreeting responded on X calling
OL,15,FHealey an "excellent defence
OL,16,Fsecretary" and that the warnings in
OL,17,Fhis resignation letter "needs to be
OL,18,Fheeded".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
