PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781197569
OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,FArmed Forces minister Al Carns told
OL,7,FTimes Radio that the DIP "is not fit
OL,8,Ffor purpose" and said that Starmer has
OL,9,F"got to sort this out".
OL,11,FMark Rutte, Secretary General of NATO
OL,12,Fhas responded at a conference saying
OL,13,Fhe respects Healey very much and that
OL,14,F"what we are seeing all over the
OL,15,Falliance is defence spending stepping
OL,16,Fup".
OL,18,FHe added: "The core task of every
OL,19,Fgovernment in the end is keeping the
OL,20,Fcountry safe".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
