OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,FLabour Peer and former head of the
OL,7,FNavy, Alan West has compared the
OL,8,Fgovernment to a sinking ship and said
OL,9,Fthat the defence settlement is a
OL,10,F"terrible error for our nation".
