PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781197569
OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,FHis resignation has brough praise from
OL,7,Fopposition MPs, with the shadow
OL,8,Fdefence secretary saying Healey had
OL,9,Fshown "integrity" by resigning and
OL,10,Ftold the prime minister he was "paying
OL,11,Fthe price" for underfunding the armed
OL,12,Fforces.
OL,14,FIn a video posted to social media,
OL,15,FJames Cartlidge said: "Whatever our
OL,16,Fpolitical differences, I have always
OL,17,Fadmired John Healey's integrity and
OL,18,Fhe's shown that in this action."
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@QO]rD@`OUsD@JO]wD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
