OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781197569
OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat leader Ed Davey
OL,7,Fcalled the resignation "a wake-up call
OL,8,Ffor Starmer and Burnham" and said that
OL,9,FLabour need to "get serious about
OL,10,Ffunding our armed forces properly".
OL,12,FLeader of the Green Party, Zack
OL,13,FPolanski wrote on X, "Labour has no
OL,14,Fserious plan to address threats we
OL,15,Fface".
OL,17,FHe said: "We must be very wary of
OL,18,Flining the pockets of arms companies
OL,19,Fwith a limitless spending bill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
