OL,3,CJohn Healey resigns as defence
OL,4,Csecretary over military spending plans
OL,6,F"Real security means traditional
OL,7,Fdefence, yes. But also resilient
OL,8,Fpublic services, a world class health
OL,9,Fservice."
OL,11,FReform UK's Robert Jenrick said "good
OL,12,Fon John Healey" and criticised the
OL,13,Fgovernment's spending priorities.
